chart.programText:
A = data('heroku.memory_quota', filter=filter('process_type', 'web')).sum(by=['app_name', 'process_type']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('heroku.memory_total', filter=filter('process_type', 'web')).sum(by=['app_name', 'process_type']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B/A*100).publish(label='C')
